extends layouts/base

block content
    p Hi #{name},
    p Please click following link to verify your email.
    table.btn.btn-primary(role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0")
        tbody
            tr
                td(align="left")
                    table(role="presentation" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0")
                        tbody
                            tr
                                td
                                    a(href=`${url}` target="_blank") Verify this email
    p This is a really simple email template. Its sole purpose is to get the recipient to click the button with no distractions.
    p Good luck! Hope it works.